    "title": "Mamaearth Capital India is Hiring: E-commerce Executive (Lead)",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Mamaearth Capital India. We are on the lookout for a dedicated E-commerce Executive to strengthen our Chennai-based team.\n\nAbout Mamaearth Capital India:\nMamaearth Capital India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Mamaearth Capital India!",
